Then we covered how to modify or customize some of the built-in endpoints.

11
00:00:33,999 --> 00:00:36,238
We learned how to add our own custom health checks,

12
00:00:36,238 --> 00:00:39,358
add custom data to the info endpoint, and lastly,

13
00:00:39,358 --> 00:00:41,809
how to add our own custom metrics.

14
00:00:41,809 --> 00:00:45,248
We finished out the module with a section on writing our

15
00:00:45,248 --> 00:00:49,328
very own custom actuator endpoints using the @endpoint

16
00:00:49,328 --> 00:00:53,311
annotation along with the @Read, @Write,

17
00:00:53,311 --> 00:00:57,978
and @DeleteOperation annotations to control whether we

18
00:00:57,978 --> 00:01:00,807
returned information or performed some action.

19
